Part 1- Business Description

Lit Pizza is a restaurant that serves personalized fire blasted pizzas, and are open seven days a week.
They have a variety of menu options such as  signature pizzas, calzones and salads.
They give you the option of creating your own personalized pizza, or customizing their signature pizzas via special instructions.
They operate in multiple states, and employ  a full time staff of team members and managers.
They require fresh ingredients, so they receive shipments of food daily, and their shelf life is watched carefully to ensure the ingredients are perfect. 
In addition, customers are given the option to join the Lit Pizza Rewards Program, which offers perks to members after a certain amount of purchases. 
